---
title: Creamy Chicken & Veggies Pie with Cheesy Parmesan-Parsnip Topping
description: Sometimes only a pie will do. Satisfy that warm and cosy craving with this rich, cheesy mash-topped number. Chicken and veggies are cooked in a creamy sauce for an explosion of flavour and a dinner that reminds us why at-home cooking is best.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66a8937a6959dc8b94ffabed-9e460ec4.jpeg
